commentBody:
Isn't time to stop pandering?
Isn't time to forget about partisan politics?
Isn't it time to work on what is good for America? 
Isn't it time to move forward?
(The election is less than one year away.)
Isn't it time to move past the impeachment fiasco?
Isn't it time to implement policy?
Isn't it time to stop gerrymandering?
Isn't it time to implement legislation?
(After three years, all we as a nation have accomplished is more divisiveness and polarization!)
Isn't it time to move on?
